dcterms:description: The Common Systems Dataset is derived from the 2013 and 2014 KBP-ESF competitions, containing data from 10 common teams that participated in both years. It includes various systems' outputs and is used for training and testing the stacking approach.
dcterms:title: Common Systems Dataset

dcterms:creator: Mihai Surdeanu
Heng Ji
dcterms:description: The All 2014 SFV Systems Dataset comprises all 65 systems that participated in the 2014 KBP Slot Filler Validation (SFV) task. It is used for evaluating the stacking approach against other ensembling methods.
dcterms:title: All 2014 SFV Systems Dataset
